The Challenge: A Grey Tsunami Is Building

- 76 million Baby Boomers are aging, straining every resource for older adults.  
- 11,000+ Boomers turn 65 every single day, with the peak hitting in 2028.  
- 44% of family caregivers report serious emotional strain from fragmented, overwhelming care planning.  
- Millennial and Gen X “sandwich generation” caregivers lose $25 billion in productivity each year while trying to juggle kids, careers, and aging parents.

The system is broken. Families are exhausted. We’re here to fix it.

---

Our Approach: Tailored Care Planning Focused on What Matters

Powered by 20+ years of senior care expertise and AI innovation, Wellderly creates holistic plans that address all the key needs to thrive:

Plan Categories**  
- Home Setting – Best living options (independent, assisted, memory care, or stay at home)  
- Enriching Care – Home care, hospice, palliative, adult day programs  
- Wellness & Social – Activity support, Silver Sneakers, clubs, read-to-kids programs  
- Transportation – Doctor trips, hair appointments, grocery runs  
- Life Easing Tools – Safety solutions, chair lifts, grab bars, pill dispensers  
- Legal & Financial – Living wills, DNRs, power of attorney, Medicaid planning  

Every plan is **activated via human support**—local Care Advisors who know your community and walk beside you.

